---
title: Southwestern-Spiced Chicken Thighs and Ranch Salad with Charred Veggies
description: Sweet peppers and corn pair perfectly with tender chicken in this tantalizing meal that comes together with our fabulous Southwestern Spice Blend. It's easy, fast and packed with flavour!
